author: Xbox
description:
Autopsy Simulator is a first-person horror-sim hybrid where players take on the role of a practice pathologist and study case files, created in collaboration with real-world forensic doctors, to help guide their dissection of anatomically accurate bodies to determine each subject’s cause of death.

Coming April 3rd to Xbox

description:
How 2 Escape series returns in a brand-new episode: Lost Submarine!

Team up with a friend to reach a lost submarine and prevent the outbreak of war. Work together on two devices to solve increasingly challenging puzzles, where each of you has your own unique role to play. 

How 2 Escape: Lost Submarine will be available in 2025 on Xbox One and Xbox Series.
